Paper: hep-th/9409080

Date: 1994-09-14

Title: A Complete Perturbative Expansion for Constrained Quantum Dynamics

Authors: P. Maraner

Comments: 18 pages, LaTex

Journal-ref: J.Phys. A28 (1995) 2939-2952

A complete perturbative expansion for the Hamiltonian describing the motionof a quantomechanical system constrained to move on an arbitrary submanifold ofits configuration space $R^n$ is obtained.